## Authoritative References

When guidelines conflict or a situation is unclear, consult:

- [WCAG 2.2 Specification](https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG22/) — W3C official
- [ARIA Authoring Practices Guide](https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/) — W3C official
- [WAI Tutorials](https://www.w3.org/WAI/tutorials/) — W3C official
- [TRUSTED_SOURCES.yaml](https://github.com/mgifford/ACCESSIBILITY.md/blob/main/examples/TRUSTED_SOURCES.yaml) — project-vetted references

---

This skill does not cover every accessibility requirement. When unsure, document the uncertainty and recommend human expert review — particularly from people with lived disability experience, whose knowledge is irreplaceable.
